WhiteFox::

She kept walking, hoping to find some bot who could tell her where 
and when she was. She stopped and paused for a moment when she 
thought she heard some noise. It might have been some bots talking. 
She wasn't sure. She checked her scanner, but it was scrambled and 
would need repairs before working properly again. She stayed tucked 
in behind a tree to wait and see what would happen.
